      • onHyperTextClicked

        public void onHyperTextClicked(String hypertext,
                               int hypertextType,
                               int datetimeType)
        This handler is called when is clicked a hyper text.
        Parameters:
        hypertext - Text of clicked hyper text
        hypertextType - Hyper text type is one of HYPERTEXT_TYPE_NONE, HYPERTEXT_TYPE_URL, HYPERTEXT_TYPE_EMAIL, HYPERTEXT_TYPE_PHONE, HYPERTEXT_TYPE_ADDRESS, HYPERTEXT_TYPE_DATETIME
        datetimeType - Date time type is one of SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_NONE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_STANDARD_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_STANDARD_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_STANDARD_DATE_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_STANDARD_TIME_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_DATE_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_TIME_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_KEYWORD_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_ENGLISH_KEYWORD_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_DATE_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_TIME_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_KEYWORD_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_KOREAN_KEYWORD_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_WESTERN_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_WESTERN_DATE_TIME, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_WESTERN_TIME_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_WESTERN_KEYWORD_DATE, SpenTextSpan.DATETIME_TYPE_WESTERN_KEYWORD_TIME
        Since:
        5.0.0
